flowRoot.flowPara: When attacking, you may change 1 of your d results to a c result.
Immediately after rolling your attack dice, you must change all of your c results to d results.
Your d results cannot be canceled by defense dice.
The defender may cancel c results before d results.
If this attack hits, the defender suffers 1 damage and, if the defender is not stressed, it also receives 1 stress token. Then cancel all dice results.
